title: North Admiral, 3 bedroom
posting_body: Gem in prime location, 2 story updated bungalow,  close to Admiral junction with tiled bath, spacious kitchen, d/w and granite counter, new LVP flooring, insulated windows and gas heat.
Large washer/dryer in unfinished basement plus storage space.
Original period fireplace and sweet TREX maintenance free deck.
NO PETS, utilities are shared, so is yard maintenance (mowing, weeding) with power mower and tools PROVIDED.
Apple and plum trees in backyard, this nicely maintained house is a gardeners delight.
Credit and income to be verified.
